sp; BUTTON_A&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 1 &lt;&lt; 7<br />&nbsp; BUTTON_B&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 1 &lt;&lt; 6<br />&nbsp; BUTTON_SELECT&nbsp; &nbsp;= 1 &lt;&lt; 5<br />&nbsp; BUTTON_START&nbsp; &nbsp; = 1 &lt;&lt; 4<br />&nbsp; BUTTON_UP&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 1 &lt;&lt; 3<br />&nbsp; BUTTON_DOWN&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 1 &lt;&lt; 2<br />&nbsp; BUTTON_LEFT&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 1 &lt;&lt; 1<br />&nbsp; BUTTON_RIGHT&nbsp; &nbsp; = 1 &lt;&lt; 0<br />&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; .rsset $0000<br />&nbsp; ButtonsHeldLastFrame .rs 1<br />&nbsp; ButtonsHeldNow .rs 1</div><br /><br />EDIT: Problem solved. I simply had to put colons after all of the names. A bit annoying, but functional.</div>

